title: oil of the fell fletcher
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This malachite-hued oil can cover up to twenty wooden sticks, and takes 10 minutes to apply. One of the sticks, chosen randomly, is transformed into a poisonous snake, which is hostile and attacks you. The rest of the sticks are transformed into arrows.